node.title: Woman dies in motorcycle crash on Auckland's North Shore
node.description: Police said the woman died at the scene, and her death will be referred to the Coroner.
node.content: ["A woman has died in a motorcycle crash on Auckland's North Shore.", "Emergency services were called to the crash near Stadium Drive in Albany at 3:25pm.", "Police said the woman died at the scene, and her death will be referred to the Coroner."]
